{
  "stem": "26731.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And at that time we realized that we want to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- let's go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People-- in fact, it was a colleague of my father's.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a judge who went, escaped, never took out for his papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He just stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We found out he had some attachment here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When he came back, he married-- it was, I guess, a friend he married right afterwards, but couldn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he just was waiting for the day he could come back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He said, I did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You will thank God that you did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Don't stay here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And but I still waited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I waited at the-- to finish the course at that special-- that school, even took the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember some care packages that arrived before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Those were the care-- the army packages, I guess, C-rations, rations for six men for one day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We loved it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then of course came, whenever you've got a package, then came the great moment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Each package had cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But it depends-- it was very important what brand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because at that time you didn't pay in mark, you paid in cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And Camel, it was the most valuable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The order was Camel, Chesterfield, Lucky Strike, Phillip Morris, Pall Mall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The last was Raleigh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were happy if it was Raleigh, but if you got a Camel, ah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was somewhat difficult, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My father was back in office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But now we are going and-- go to the black market and pay cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That wasn't legal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father never-- he suspected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, you'll never admit it, that we have occasionally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember there was one brand which he kept for himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was Phillip Morris he liked.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
